  GET  /api/problems/suggest      ← single suggestion based on profile
  POST /api/submissions           ← accept code, write pending row, enqueue job
  GET  /api/submissions/:id       ← poll verdict
  GET  /api/submissions/history   ← paginated history
  GET  /api/progress/today        ← daily summary (solved, time spent, streak)
  GET  /api/streak                ← current + longest streak

Dependencies to implement first:
  packages/storage   ← pgx connection pool, problem queries, submission queries
  packages/queue     ← asynq client, job type definitions

Verdict in Milestone 2 can be mock (no real Docker execution yet — that is Milestone 6).
